Reserve 2 of the wafers; set aside. Coarsely crush remaining 10 wafers. Spoon crushed wafers into each of two dessert dishes. Mix water and coffee; drizzle over crushed wafers. Top each with contents of one pudding snack cup, 2 Tbsp. whipped topping, 1/2 tsp. cocoa powder and 1 reserved wafer. Serve immediately or cover and refrigerate until ready to serve.